<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brightness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brightness,</orth> clear light, splendor: <cit><quote>swear that b. doth not grace the day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 150.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 150, 4</bibl></cit>. <emph>in her</emph> (fortune's) <cit><quote>ray and b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 47</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the b. of her cheek would shame those stars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 19</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>